# Testing

- Minimum coverage: 80%. Include unit, integration, and E2E tests.
- TDD workflow: write a failing test first (RED) → minimal implementation (GREEN) → refactor (IMPROVE) → verify coverage.
- Fix the implementation, not the tests — unless the test itself is wrong.
- Check test isolation and correct mocks when diagnosing failures.
